OL,7,FThere are calls for swifter action
OL,8,Fagainst animal cruelty following
OL,9,Fsecret filming at a Warwickshire
OL,10,Fabattoir, as ITV News Central reporter
OL,11,FPablo Taylor reports...
OL,13,FResidents in a Warwickshire village
OL,14,Fhave been protesting outside of an
OL,15,Fabattoir after a video was released
OL,16,Fonline showing what they say is
OL,17,Fevidence of animal abuse.
