OL,7,FAustralian filmmaker and animal rights
OL,8,Factivist, Joey Carbstrong, installed
OL,9,Fsecret cameras in a halal
OL,10,Fslaughterhouse in Arley.
OL,12,FHe says he filmed around 200 hours of
OL,13,Ffootage last summer, and claims to
OL,14,Fhave found multiple instances of
OL,15,Fpossible illegality at the abattoir in
OL,16,Frelation to the rough handling of the
OL,17,Fanimals and ineffective restraints
OL,18,Fduring slaughter.
