OL,5,Cfilming
OL,7,FThe footage appears to show sheep and
OL,8,Fgoats being killed and some
OL,9,Fdismembered whilst still showing signs
OL,10,Fof life.
OL,12,FSome animals also appear to be
OL,13,Fforcefully manhandled and hit by
OL,14,Fworkers.
OL,16,FThe slaughterhouse, owned by T&S
OL,17,FAbattoir, is being investigated by the
OL,18,FFood Standards Agency.
OL,20,FThree workers from the slaughterhouse
OL,21,Fhave been fired.
