OL,7,FThe footage formed the basis of a
OL,8,Freport by Jenny L. Mace, an associate
OL,9,Flecturer at the University of
OL,10,FWinchester, who specialises in animal
OL,11,Fwelfare, behaviour, ethics, and law.
OL,13,FUnder government regulations, halal
OL,14,Fslaughterhouses must wait a minimum of
OL,15,F20 seconds after cutting sheep and
OL,16,Fgoats to ensure they have lost
OL,17,Fconsciousness.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/17
