OL,8,Fthat, according to her, that wasn't
OL,9,Fhappening. She said: "The staff, the
OL,10,Fslaughter is supposed to be
OL,11,Fsystematically checking for a lack of
OL,12,Fconsciousness in the sheep.
OL,14,F"It was clear that there were no
OL,15,Fsystematic checks going on for
OL,16,Fconsciousness in the sheep before they
OL,17,Fwere being moved.
