OL,7,FThe MP for Nuneaton Jodie Gosling
OL,8,Fraised the issue in the House of
OL,9,FCommons saying: "Footage, released
OL,10,Fyesterday (5th March), appears to show
OL,11,F200 horrific hours of repeated animal
OL,12,Fabuse at an abattoir in my
OL,13,Fconstituency.
OL,15,F"I have been working with residents
OL,16,Fand a multitude of agencies to try and
OL,17,Fensure safety and compliance long
OL,18,Fbefore my election to this place.
